OL,3,CLocal Elections 2026: The results on
OL,4,Cthe Isle of Wight as the island decides
OL,6,FOn the Isle of Wight Reform UK are
OL,7,Fhoping for a major breakthrough in the
OL,8,Flocal elections.
OL,10,FThe island has been run by coalition
OL,11,Fof independents and Green councillors,
OL,12,Fknown as the Alliance Group, since the
OL,13,Flast election in 2021.
OL,15,FLike Hampshire County Council, every
OL,16,Fseat is up for election, and in recent
OL,17,Fyears, no party has been able to get
OL,18,Fenough seats to take overall control.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G1/6
