OL,3,CLocal Elections 2026: The results on
OL,4,Cthe Isle of Wight as the island decides
OL,6,FIslanders elected a mix of councillors
OL,7,Fat the last election, with the
OL,8,FConservatives and independents taking
OL,9,Fthe largest number of seats.
OL,11,FUse our interactive map to see the
OL,12,Fresults of each seat in the Isle of
OL,13,FWight elections.
OL,15,FThe Tories, like Reform UK, will be
OL,16,Fhoping to make gains, whilst
OL,17,Findependent candidates and smaller
OL,18,Fparties will be looking to hold their
OL,19,Fseats.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G2/6
